name: Kitchacell
description:
Made in 72 hours for Mini Jam 94: Baking

Chase high scores across several unique minigames, try to beat your high score and collect all of the palettes! All minigames use only the left and right arrows, interact with menus using 'z' or 'x'

Inspired by warioware, and early PSP games!


Move : Left Arrow/Right Arrow

Interact : 'z' or 'x'

Chase high scores across several different minigames of increasing intensity. Every game uses only the left / right arrows for their controls. How fast can you get?

Try to unlock every colour palette!

Music, Art, Programming by Louie Chapman - @0xFFB3
